title: Very Captivating Res Lease in Austin. 3 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: ['Rent one of the best houses in Texas!', 'This amazing 3-bedroom single-story home is located in Northeast Austin close to the North Austin tech hub!', 'Once inside, you will discover a well-designed open floorplan with tile flooring and a fully equipped kitchen complete with elegant dark wood cabinets, subway tile backsplash, and granite countertops.', 'All 3 bedrooms are spacious and are outfitted with carpet flooring with easy access into one of the 2 bathrooms.', 'W/D hookups and a privately fenced backyard are also available, come check it out and apply today!', '**', 'In-person tours required (no exceptions)', '**All renters are enrolled in the resident benefits package.', '--to set up a viewing--', 'Call/Text/Email ANYTIME!', 'Cristian Argueta', 'show contact info', '(ask for ID# 4802406)', 'All City Real Estate Company', 'Have other properties available....', '(Houses, Duplexes, Apartments, Condos, All Areas)', 'Please be Aware of SCAMS...', 'Do NOT reply to this ad, please call/text for a fast response.', 'Listed By: Benjamin Doherty, Sunroom Rentals Texas, LLC']
